[Episode 22]

22
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:39,639
- Put this towel on your forehead.
- But I use it to wipe my feet.

23
00:01:39,639 --> 00:01:42,980
You're dying, stop minding such a petty thing.

24
00:01:42,980 --> 00:01:46,559
- Fine!
- Where are the test results?

25
00:01:46,559 --> 00:01:48,430
On the table.

26
